<p>For example, I'm setting the data like following to redis.</p>  <pre><code>SET "projects:views:PROJECT_NAME1" 17 SET "projects:views:PROJECT_NAME2" 13 SET "projects:views:PROJECT_NAME3" 21 </code></pre>  <p><code>PROJECT_NAME</code> differs according to project record name that I get from relational database.</p>  <p>How can I sort all "project:views:*" by value. In this example our output should be</p>  <pre><code>PROJECT_NAME3 21 PROJECT_NAME1 17 PROJECT_NAME2 13 </code></pre>